org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.admin

Interface GemfireAdminOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGemfireAdminOperations, FunctionGemfireAdminTemplate, RestHttpGemfireAdminTemplate

    public interface GemfireAdminOperations
    The GemfireAdminOperations interface defines a set of operations to define schema objects in a remote Apache Geode or Pivotal GemFire cluster.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    See Also:
    DiskStore, Region, Index, IndexDefinition, RegionDefinition, SchemaObjectDefinition
